**Cleansing Notice Summary:**  
- **Shares Issued:** 9,789,195 fully paid ordinary shares issued on 2 July 2025 via conversion of vested performance/service rights.  
- **Disclosure Exemption:** Issued under Section 708A(5)(e) of Corporations Act (no Part 6D.2 disclosure).  
- **Compliance:** Company confirms adherence to ongoing reporting obligations (Ch. 2M, ss. 674/674A).  

*No material trading or capital structure impact identified (routine conversion of existing rights).*
